      "message": "We can add something like that, but let\u0027s save it for a future addition to this to keep things simple for now.  I can imagine adding a \"flaky\" category (since we have so many) and having a separate bot to run those tests just to report stats on how often they fail.  Similarly, we could have a \"failing\" category with a bot which verifies that those tests actually fail and notifies us when they don\u0027t.",
